ReadCashReceiptDetailStatus
data.value: select top(1) CRDETAIL_STAT_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_CR_DETAIL_STAT where (CRDETAIL_STAT_ID = @crdetailStatId) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadCashReceiptSourceType
data.value: select top(1) CR_SRCE_TYPE_ID, CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_CRSRC_TYPE where (CODE = @code) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadCashReceiptStatus
data.value: select top(1) CR_STATUS_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_CR_STATUS where (CR_STATUS_ID = @crStatusId) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadCashReceiptType
data.value: select top(1) CRTYPE_ID, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_CR_TYPE where (CRTYPE_ID = @crtypeId) and (EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate) and (DISCONTINUE_DATE > @effectiveDate)

data.name: ReadCollectionType1
data.value: select top(1) COLLECTION_TYPE_ID, CODE, EFFECTIVE_DATE, DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_COLLTN_TYPE where CODE = @code
